### 1) Request OTP
POST http://localhost:8080/request-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{ "phone": "+60120000000" }

### 2) Verify OTP (paste code from server console)
POST http://localhost:8080/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{ "phone": "+60120000000", "otp": "PASTE_OTP_HERE" }

### 3) Child sends location (use token from step 2)
POST http://localhost:8080/locations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_JWT_HERE

{ "lat": 3.139, "lng": 101.686 }

### 4) Parent fetches latest location (parent needs its own JWT too, or just reuse child for now)
GET http://localhost:8080/locations/+60120000000
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_JWT_HERE
